        message_id,
        message_number,
        message_timestamp,
        ers_message_type_id,
        message_year,
        relevant_year,
        sequence_number,
        ers_activity_id,
        departure_timestamp,
        fishing_timestamp,
        start_latitude,
        start_latitude_sggdd,
        start_longitude,

        target_species_fiskeridir_id,

        fiskeridir_vessel_id,
        vessel_building_year,
        vessel_call_sign,
        vessel_call_sign_ers,
        vessel_engine_building_year,
        vessel_engine_power,
        vessel_gross_tonnage_1969,
        vessel_gross_tonnage_other,

        vessel_county_code,

        vessel_length,
        vessel_length_group,
        vessel_length_group_code,

        vessel_rebuilding_year,
        vessel_registration_id,
        vessel_registration_id_ers,
        vessel_valid_until,
        vessel_width
